.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstreaming%2Fhow-to-watch-olympics-live-stream-paris-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewatch%20the%202024%20Olympic%20Games%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20NBC%20and%20Telemundo%2C%20or%20stream%20it%20on%20Peacock.%20Tens%20of%20thousands%20also%20watch%20the%20games%20in%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20tickets%20varies%20by%20event%20and%20date%2C%20with%20tickets%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftickets.paris2024.org%2Fobj%2Fmedia%2FFR-Paris2024%2Fticket-prices.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2024%20Games%3C%2Fa%3E%20ranging%20from%20%E2%82%AC24%20to%20%E2%82%AC980%2C%20or%20about%20%2426%20to%20%241%2C066%20USD.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftickets-paris-2024-olympics-opening-ceremony-sticker-shock-sold-out-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOlympics%20opening%20ceremony%20tickets%3C%2Fa%3E%20cost%20nearly%20%243%2C000%20and%20were%20almost%20completely%20sold%20out%20by%20January%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22096d5e93-8e9d-45e3-8907-b170a54f332f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20history%20of%20the%20Olympics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Olympics%20are%20rooted%20in%20the%20Ancient%20Olympic%20Games%2C%20which%20started%20as%20early%20as%20776%20BC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20Olympics%20were%20held%20in%20Olympia%2C%20a%20town%20on%20the%20Peloponnese%20peninsula%20in%20ancient%20Greece.%20The%20ancient%20games%20were%20created%20as%20something%20of%20a%20religious%20festival%20meant%20to%20honor%20Zeus%2C%20and%20occurred%20every%20four%20years%20for%20over%201%2C000%20years%2C%20according%20to%20the%20IOC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ancient%20Olympic%20games%20looked%20markedly%20different%20from%20today's%20games.%20For%20example%2C%20competitors%20had%20to%20be%20naked%20during%20competitions%2C%20and%20some%20athletes%20died%20competing%20in%20combat%20sports%20like%20boxing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20modern%20iteration%20of%20the%20games%20began%20in%201896%20in%20Athens%2C%20Greece%2C%20after%20Pierre%20de%20Coubertin%20created%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Folympics-inc-inside-the-business-of-the-ioc%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInternational%20Olympic%20Committee%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%201894.%20The%20games%20have%20expanded%20over%20the%20past%20century%20and%20a%20half%20to%20become%20the%20Olympics%20we%20know%20today.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-the-olympics-and-paralympics-are-separate-events-2016-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Paralympic%20Games%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20later%20introduced%20in%201960.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20black-and-white%20photograph%20shows%20eight%20male%20athletes%20performing%20on%20eight%20sets%20of%20parallel%20bars%20in%20front%20of%20a%20large%20crowd%20of%20spectators%20at%20the%201896%20Olympics%20in%20Athens%2C%20Greece.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F57ac9807dd089575178b48a4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222134%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20very%20first%20modern%20Olympic%20Games%20were%20held%20in%20Athens%2C%20Greece%2C%20in%201896.%20%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20symbols%20associated%20with%20the%20games%20have%20become%20iconic%20over%20the%20past%20century%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20the%20Olympic%20rings.%20The%20rings%20are%20made%20up%20of%20five%20interlocking%20circles%20in%20blue%2C%20yellow%2C%20black%2C%20green%2C%20and%20red.%20The%20rings%20also%20appear%20on%20the%20Olympic%20flag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Olympic%20Charter%2C%20which%20codifies%20the%20principals%20and%20rules%20of%20the%20Olympics%2C%20states%20that%20the%20symbol%20of%20the%20rings%20%26quot%3Bexpresses%20the%20activity%20of%20the%20Olympic%20Movement%20and%20represents%20the%20union%20of%20the%20five%20continents%20and%20the%20meeting%20of%20athletes%20fr