%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222831%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMichael%20Phelps%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20iconic%20athletes%20and%20Olympians%20of%20all%20time%2C%20and%20has%20won%20more%20medals%20than%20any%20other%20competitor.%3Cp%3EGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%202024%20games%20in%20Paris%20will%20also%20feature%20some%20of%20the%20fastest%20athletes%20in%20the%20world%2C%20from%20sprinters%20like%20Sha'Carri%20Richardson%20and%20Noah%20Lyles%2C%20to%20swimmers%20like%20Katie%20Ledecky%20and%20Caeleb%20Dressel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOlympic%20athletes%20vary%20in%20age.%20There%20is%20no%20official%20minimum%20age%20requirement%20for%20the%20Olympics%2C%20though%20some%20sports%20have%20minimum%20age%20requirements.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20minimum%20age%20to%20compete%20in%20Olympic%20gymnastics%20is%2016%2C%20while%20Olympic%20swimming%20has%20no%20minimum%20age%20requirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20youngest%20athlete%20in%20the%202024%20Olympics%20will%20be%2011-year-old%20Zheng%20Haohao%2C%20a%20skateboarder%20from%20China.%20The%20youngest%20member%20of%20Team%20USA%20is%2016-year-old%20gymnast%20Hezly%20Rivera%2C%20who%20will%20be%20competing%20alongside%20Biles%2C%20Suni%20Lee%2C%20Jordan%20Chiles%2C%20and%20Jade%20Carey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20oldest%20athlete%20in%20the%202024%20Olympics%20will%20be%2059-year-old%20Steffen%20Peters%2C%20a%20US%20equestrian%20team%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20youngest%20confirmed%20athlete%20in%20modern%20Olympic%20history%20was%2010-year-old%20Dimitrios%20Loundras%2C%20who%20competed%20for%20Greece%20on%20the%20team%20parallel%20bars%20event%20in%20the%201896%20games%20in%20Athens%20and%20won%20a%20bronze%20medal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20oldest%20athlete%20in%20modern%20Olympic%20history%20was%2072-year-old%20Oscar%20Swahn%2C%20a%20shooter%20from%20Sweden%20who%20won%20six%20medals%20%E2%80%94%20including%20three%20gold%20%E2%80%94%20throughout%20his%20Olympic%20career%20in%20the%20early%2020th%20