20the%20Titanic%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20RMS%20Titanic%2C%20a%20British%20passenger%20ship%20operated%20by%20the%20White%20Star%20Line%2C%20set%20sail%20on%20its%20infamous%20voyage%20on%20April%2010%2C%201912.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%202%2C000%20people%20were%20aboard%20the%20ship%20when%20it%20collided%20with%20an%20iceberg%20and%20sank%20during%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20April%2015%2C%201912.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20all%20the%20passengers%20aboard%20the%20Titanic%2C%20about%20700%20people%20made%20it%20into%20lifeboats.%20Most%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftitanic-famous-survivors-victims-2018-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETitanic%20victims%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20did%20not%20make%20it%20onto%20a%20lifeboat%20either%20drowned%2C%20went%20down%20with%20the%20ship%2C%20or%20froze%20to%20death%20in%20the%20Atlantic%20Ocean%20as%20they%20waited%20to%20be%20rescued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20survival%20rate%20for%20first-class%20male%20passengers%20aboard%20Titanic%20was%20just%2033%25%2C%20according%20to%20the%20study%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F27971166%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BTitanic%3A%20A%20Statistical%20Exploration%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20making%20Williams'%20story%20of%20survival%20all%20the%20more%20extraordinary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERichard%20Norris%20Williams%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20notable%20people%20who%20survived%20the%20Titanic%20sinking.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223331%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Richard%20Norris%20Williams%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a1c2976979d73718231ec0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224287%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERichard%20Norris%20Williams.%3Cp%3EGeorge%20Rinhart%2FCorbis%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWilliams%2C%20commonly%20known%20as%20R.%20Norris%20Williams%2C%20was%20born%20on%20January%2029%2C%201891%2C%20in%20Geneva%