eep%20it%20in%20tip-top%20shape.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrooklinen%20has%20a%20flexible%20return%20policy%20and%20will%20accept%20most%20products%20up%20to%20365%20days%20after%20purchase.%20While%20there%20is%20a%20%249.95%20return%20fee%20to%20ship%20items%20back%2C%20this%20can%20be%20avoided%20if%20you%20are%20near%20one%20of%20the%20brand's%20retail%20stores%2C%20which%20is%20how%20I%20returned%20the%20mid-plush%20pillow.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%20to%20consider%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20downside%20to%20this%20pillow%20is%20its%20high%20price%20point%20(though%20I%20will%20note%20that%20it's%20on%20par%20with%20most%20of%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-pillow%5C%22%3Etop%20picks%3C%2Fa%3E).%20Depending%20on%20the%20size%20and%20support%20you%20choose%2C%20it%20ranges%20from%20%24109%20to%20%24149.%20I%20started%20off%20with%20one%20pillow%20to%20see%20how%20I'd%20like%20it%20before%20getting%20another%2C%20which%20could%20be%20a%20good%20option%20for%20anyone%20on%20a%20budget%20like%20I%20am.%20If%20you%20like%20to%20sleep%20on%20a%20pillow%20stack%20like%20me%2C%20I'd%20recommend%20placing%20the%20Brooklinen%20pillow%20over%20a%20more%20budget-friendly%20option.%20This%20will%20give%20you%20the%20airy%20softness%20you're%20looking%20for%20and%20keep%20your%20head%20supported.%20However%2C%20the%20brand%20does%20offer%20discounts%20of%2010%25%20to%2015%25%20for%20packs%20of%20two%20or%20four.%20My%20pillows%20still%20feel%20brand%20new%20after%20three%20years%2C%20making%20them%20an%20investment%20I%20feel%20good%20about.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20Business%20Insider%20reviewer%20who%20also%20tested%20the%20Brooklinen%20down%20pillow%20noted%20an%20initial%20down%20smell%20after%20opening%20that%20dissipated%20after%20a%20few%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20are%20your%20alter