-cr-revenue-up-15-124072401278_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fbikaji-foods-q1-result-net-profit-rises-40-to-rs-58-06-cr-revenue-up-15-124072401278_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fbikaji-foods-q1-result-net-profit-rises-40-to-rs-58-06-cr-revenue-up-15-124072401278_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BFiring%20Should%20Scare%20Salman%20Khan%26quot%3B%3A%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi's%20Brother%20Told%20Shooter%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFire%20shots%20in%20such%20a%20manner%20that%20it%20scares%20Bollywood%20superstar%20Salman%20Khan%20--%20this%20was%20the%20blunt%2C%20one-line%20message%20given%20by%20jailed%20gangster%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi's%20younger%20brother%20Anmol%20to%20one%20of%20the%20gunmen%20involved%20in%20the%20shooting%20outside%20the%20actor's%20Mumbai%20home%2C%20police%20said%20in%20a%20chargesheet%20filed%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mumbai%20police's%20crime%20branch%2C%20probing%20the%20sensational%20firing%20case%2C%20earlier%20this%20month%20filed%20a%201%2C735-page%20chargesheet%20before%20the%20special%20Maharashtra%20Control%20of%20Organised%20Crime%20Act%20(MCOCA)%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConspiracy%20of%20firing%20at%20the%20actor's%20house%20was%20hatched%20with%20the%20intention%20of%20establishing%20a%20stronghold%20and%20supremacy%20in%20the%20country's%20financial%20capital%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20getting%20pecuniary%20and%20other%20advantages%20for%20the%20Bishnoi%20gang%2C%20according%20to%20the%20chargesheet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chargesheet%20included%20various%20investigation%20papers%20incorporated%20in%20three%20volumes.%20One%20such%20document%20is%20the%20transcript%20of%20an%20audio%20chat%20between%20Anmol%20Bishnoi%20and%20arrested%20shooter%20Vickykumar%20Gupta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20of%20the%20conversations%2C%20Anmol%20Bishnoi%20is%20heard%20instructing%20Gupta%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20firing%20thoughtfully%20and%20everywhere%2C%20even%20if%20it%20takes%20more%20than%20a%20minute%20and%20should%20be%20done%20in%20such%20a%20manner%20that%20it%20scares%20'Bhai'%20(Salman%20Khan)%2C%20the%20chargesheet%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20he%20asks%20Gupta%20if%20he%20smokes.%20When%20the%20latter%20replies%20in%20the%20affirmative%2C%20Anmol%20Bishnoi%20tells%20him%20to%20smoke%20while%20firing%20so%20that%20he%20comes%20across%20as%20a%20fearless%20individual%20in%20CCTV%20cameras%20installed%20in%20the%20area%2C%20according%20to%20the%20voluminous%20police%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20will%20create%20history%20by%20doing%20this%20job%20and%20your%20name%20will%20be%20there%20in%20all%20newspapers%20and%20other%20media%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%2C%20citing%20their%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20motorbike-borne%20individuals%2C%20Gupta%20and%20Sagar%20Pal%2C%20had%20fired%20multiple%20shots%20outside%20Mr%20Khan's%20home%20in%20Galaxy%20Apartment%20in%20Bandra%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20April%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%2C%20along%20with%20three%20others%20--%20Sonukumar%20Bishnoi%2C%20Mohammad%20Rafiq%20Choudhary%20and%20Harpal%20Singh%20--%20are%20currently%20in%20judicial%20custody%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELawrence%20Bishnoi%2C%20Anmol%20and%20one%20Rawtaran%20Bishnoi%20have%20been%20shown%20as%20wanted%20accused%20in%20the%20chargesheet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721840760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F27sv43cg_salman-khan_625x300_17_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffiring-should-scare-salman-khan