shooting-motive-still-unknown-working-tirelessly%2Famp_articleshow%2F111994322.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BKhalistanis%20Have%20Polluted%20Canada%2C%26quot%3B%20Says%20Indian-Origin%20MP%20After%20Threats%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20prominent%20Canadian%20MP%20of%20Indian%20origin%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20the%20country%20was%20being%20%26quot%3Bpolluted%26quot%3B%20by%20Khalistani%20extremists%20who%20were%20%26quot%3Babusing%26quot%3B%20the%20freedoms%20guaranteed%20under%20the%20Charter%20of%20Rights%2C%20days%20after%20a%20Hindu%20temple%20was%20vandalised%20in%20Edmonton.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20rising%20Hinduphobia%20in%20Canada%2C%20the%20BAPS%20Swaminarayan%20Mandir%20was%20vandalised%20with%20alleged%20hateful%20and%20anti-India%20graffiti%20on%20Monday%20morning%20in%20Edmonton%20in%20Alberta%20state%2C%20about%203%2C400%20km%20west-northwest%20of%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandra%20Arya%2C%20a%20Member%20of%20Parliament%20from%20Nepean%20in%20the%20House%20of%20Commons%2C%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20his%20X%20account%20that%20separatist%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%20of%20Sikhs%20for%20Justice%20released%20a%20video%20demanding%20that%20Arya%20and%20his%20Hindu-Canadian%20friends%20go%20back%20to%20India%20after%20he%20(Arya)%20condemned%20the%20vandalism%20of%20the%20Hindu%20temple%20and%20other%20acts%20of%20hate%20and%20violence%20by%20Khalistan%20supporters%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20Hindus%20have%20come%20to%20our%20wonderful%20country%20Canada%20from%20all%20parts%20of%20the%20world.%20From%20every%20country%20in%20South%20Asia%2C%20many%20countries%20in%20Africa%20and%20Caribbean%2C%20and%20many%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20world%2C%20we%20have%20come%20here%20and%20Canada%20is%20our%20land%2C%26quot%3B%20Arya%2C%20a%20member%20of%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau's%20Liberal%20Party%2C%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20made%20and%20continue%20to%20make%20immense%20positive%20and%20productive%20contributions%20to%20the%20socio-economic%20development%20of%20Canada.%20With%20our%20long%20history%20of%20Hindu%20culture%20and%20heritage%2C%20we%20have%20enriched%20the%20multicultural%20fabric%20of%20Canada%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20land%20is%20being%20polluted%20by%20Khalistani%20extremists%20abusing%20our%20freedoms%20guaranteed%20by%20our%20Canadian%20Charter%20of%20Rights%2C%26quot%3B%20Arya%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArya's%20statement%20comes%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20severe%20strain%20in%20India-Canada%20ties%20over%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistan%20extremist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20who%20was%20gunned%20down%20in%20Surrey%2C%20British%20Columbia%2C%20in%20June%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIn%20response%20to%20my%20condemnation%20of%20the%20vandalism%20of%20the%20Hindu%20temple%20BAPS%20Swaminarayan%20Mandir%20in%20Edmonton%20and%20other%20acts%20of%20hate%20and%20violence%20by%20Khalistan%20supporters%20in%20Canada%2C%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%20of%20Sikhs%20for%20Justice%20has%20released%20a%20video%20demanding%20me%20and%20my%20Hindu-Canadian...%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FvMhnN45rc1%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FvMhnN45rc1%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Chandra%20Arya%20(%40AryaCanada)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAryaCanada%2Fstatus%2F1816045238965645689%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2024%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20came%20under%20severe%20strain%20following%20Trudeau's%20allegations%20in%20September%20last%20year%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bpotential%26quot%3B%20involvement%20of%20Indian%20agents%20in%20Nijjar's%20killing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20maintaining%20that%20the%20main%20issue%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20is%20that%20of%20Canada%20giving%20space%20to%20pro-Khalistan%20elements%20operating%20from%20Canadian%20soil%20with%20impunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20repeatedly%20conveyed%20its%20%26quot%3Bdeep%20concerns%26quot%3B%20to%20Canada%20and%20New%20Delhi%20expects%20Ottawa%20to%20take%20strong%20action%20against%20those%20elements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20vandalism%20at%20the%20BAPS%20temple%20was%20criticised%20by%20other%20local%20elected%20representatives%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Consulate%20General%20of%20India%20in%20Vancouver%20had%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20on%20Tuesday%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20condemn%20the%20defacing%20of%20BAPS%20Shri%20Swaminarayan%20Mandir%20in%20%23Edmonton%20with%20anti-India%20graffiti.%20We%20have%20requested%20the%20Canadian%20authorities%20to%20investigate%20the%20incident%20and%20take%20prompt%20action%20against%20the%20perpetrators.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20reaction%20as%20yet%20from%20the%20BAPS%20-%20the%20Bochasanwasi%20Aksharpurushottam%20Swaminarayan%20Sanstha%2C%20the%20organisation%20that%20runs%20the%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721835360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fb6kb01h_chandra-arya_625x300_24_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-origin-canadian-mp-receives-threat-from-khalistani-extremists-after-temple-vandalism-incident-6179853%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20prominent%20Canadian%20MP%20of%20Indian%20origin%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20the%20country%20was%20being%20%26quot%3Bpolluted%26quot%3B%20by%20Khalistani%20extremists%20who%20were%20%26quot%3Babusing%26quot%3B%20the%20freedoms%20guaranteed%20under%20the%20Charter%20of%20Rights%2C%20days%20after%20a%20Hindu%20temple%20was%20vandalised%20in%20Edmonton.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-origin-canadian-mp-receives-threat-from-khalistani-extremists-after-temple-vandalism-incident-6179853%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-origin-canadian-mp-receives-threat-from-khalistani-extremists-after-temple-vandalism-incident-6179853%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-origin-canadian-mp-receives-threat-from-khalistani-extremists-after-temple-vandalism-incident-6179853%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BExtra%20Special%26quot%3B%3A%20Kargil%20War%20Hero%20On%20Son%20Commanding%20His%20Former%20Division%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20quarter%20of%20a%20century%20after%20India%20secured%20a%20victory%20for%20the%20ages%20in%20the%20Kargil%20War%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20challenging%20high-altitude%20battles%20ever%20fought%2C%20the%20division%20which%20led%20the%20charge%20has%20another%20major%20reason%20to%20celebrate.%20Major%20General%20Sachin%20Malik%20is%20now%20commanding%20the%208%20Mountain%20Division%2C%20which%20had%20led%20the%20charge%20in%20the%20Kargil%20War%20under%20the%20overall%20leadership%20of%20his%20father%2C%20General%20(Retired)%20VP%20Malik%2C%20who%20was%20the%20Army%20chief%20at%20the%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeneral%20VP%20Malik%20had%20also%20once%20commanded%20the%208%20Mountain%20Division%20and%20the%20father%20and%20son%20are%20now%20in%20Dras%20to%20mark%20the%2025th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20Kargil%20Vijay%20Diwas%20on%20Friday.%20That%20is%20where%20NDTV%20caught%20up%20with%20them%20for%20an%20exclusive%20conversation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%2025th%20anniversary%2C%20which%20is%20a%20special%20occasion.%20I%20always%20come%20here%20to%20pay%20homage%20to%20the%20officers%20and%20men%20who%20were%20killed%20in%20action%20during%20the%20war%20and%20also%20to%20remember%20all%20the%20good%20work%20that%20our%20Army%20did.%20This%20year%2C%20it%20has%20also%20become%20special%20because%20Sachin%20is%20here%20and%20he%20is%20commanding%20the%20same%20division%20that%20I%20did%2C%20at%20the%20same%20place%20where%20we%20fought%20the%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20General%20VP%20Malik%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20challenges%20in%20commanding%20the%208%20Mountain%20Division%2C%20which%20works%20in%20difficult%20conditions%20right%20on%20the%20line%20of%20control%2C%20Major%20General%20Sachin%20Malik%20said%20he%20looks%20at%20it%20as%20a%20privilege%20as%20well%20as%20a%20huge%20responsibility.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20huge%20privilege%20to%20command%20the%208%20Mountain%20Division%2C%20which%20is%20known%20as%20the%20'Forever%20in%20Operations'%20division%20-%20it%20has%20always%20been%20in%20operation%20right%20from%20raising%20(in%201963).%20While%20we%20are%20commemorating%20the%20Rajat%20Jayanti%20of%20the%20Kargil%20War%2C%20we%20have%20to%20remember%20that%20the%20bulk%20of%20my%20division%20remains%20committed%20and%20deployed%20on%20the%20line%20of%20control%20to%20ensure%20nothing%20of%20the%20sort%20ever%20happens%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20Major%20General%20Malik%20asserted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20thing%20that%20comes%20to%20mind%20is%20the%20huge%20responsibility.%20These%20peaks...%20a%20lot%20of%20blood%20has%20been%20shed%20on%20them%20and%20there%20is%20no%20way%20we%20will%20ever%20allow%20anybody%20to%20do%20that%20ever%20again.%20So%20we%20have%20to%20always%20remain%20absolutely%20alert%2C%20we%20have%20to%20remain%20ready%20for%20anything%20and%20we%20have%20to%20ensure%20nothing%20of%20that%20nature%20happens%20ever%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajor%20General%20Sachin%20Malik%20took%20over%20as%20the%2042nd%20General%20Officer%20Commanding%20of%20the%20Mountain%20Division%20in%20February.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kargil%20War%20was%20fought%20between%20May%20and%20July%201999%20when%20intruders%20from%20Pakistan%20occupied%20positions%20on%20the%20Indian%20side%20of%20the%20LoC.%20The%20Indian%20Army%20and%20Air%20Force%20valiantly%20fought%20them%20off%20and%20recaptured%20many%20strategic%20posts%2C%20forcing%20a%20withdrawal%20from%20the%20remaining%20ones.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721835300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Foa54am6_general-vp-malik-sachin-malik_625x300_24_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkargil-war-general-vp-malik-major-general-sachin-malik-extra-special-kargil-war-hero-on-son-commanding-his-former-division-6179745%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20quarter%20of%20a%20century%20after%20India%20secured%20a%20victory%20for%20the%20ages%20in%20the%20Kargil%20War%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20challenging%20high-altitude%20battles%20ever%20fought%2C%20the%20division%20which%20led%20the%20charge%20has%20another%20major%20reason%20to%20celebrate.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkargil-war-general-vp-malik-major-general-sachin-malik-extra-special-kargil-war-hero-on-son-commanding-his-former-division-6179745%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkargil-war-general-vp-malik-major-general-sachin-malik-extra-special-kargil-war-hero-on-son-commanding-his-former-division-6179745%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkargil-war-general-vp-malik-major-general-sachin-malik-extra-special-kargil-war-hero-on-son-commanding-his-former-division-6179745%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sonam%20admits%20to%20being%20'the%20most%20judgy%20human%20being'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721834528000%2C%22visual%