rt%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Rajasthan%20Police's%20role%20in%20the%20encounter%20of%20gangster%20Anandpal%20will%20be%20investigated%2C%20a%20special%20court%20in%20Jodhpur%20ruled%20today%2C%20rejecting%20the%20CBI's%20closure%20report%20of%202020.%20The%20four%20police%20officers%20who%20took%20part%20in%20the%20encounter%20will%20be%20investigated%20for%20murder%2C%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2024%2C%202017%2C%20Anandpal%20was%20killed%20in%20a%20village%20in%20Churu%2C%20in%20what%20the%20police%20claimed%20was%20an%20encounter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gangster%2C%20who%20was%20hiding%20in%20a%20second%20floor%20room%20of%20a%20house%2C%20had%20fired%20on%20the%20police%20team%20with%20automatic%20weapons.%20He%20died%20in%20retaliatory%20firing%2C%20the%20police%20has%20contended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20matter%20became%20controversial%2C%20then%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20government%20asked%20the%20CBI%20to%20investigate.%20The%20CBI%20upheld%20the%20police%20report.%20But%20Anand%20Pal's%20family%2C%20led%20by%20his%20wife%20Raj%20Kanwar%2C%20filed%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20Jodhpur%20court%20against%20the%20agency's%20closure%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20seven%20years%2C%20the%20court%20has%20rejected%20the%20closure%20report%20in%20view%20of%20the%20evidence%20presented%20by%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMedical%20evidence%20suggested%20that%20Anandpal's%20body%C2%A0%20bore%20injures%20indicating%20beating.%20The%20bullet%20wounds%2C%2011%20of%20them%2C%20indicated%20that%20he%20was%20shot%20from%20close%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20had%20suggested%20they%20never%20went%20to%20the%20terrace%20where%20Anandpal%20was%20hiding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Anandpal's%20lawyer%20presented%20his%20brother%20Rupinder%20as%20a%20key%20witness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERupinder%20had%20led%20the%20police%20team%20to%20his%20brother's%20hideout%20to%20get%20him%20arrested.%20He%20told%20the%20court%20that%20he%20went%20to%20the%20terrace%20with%20the%20police%20and%20asked%20Anandpal%20to%20surrender.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20his%20brother%20was%20unharmed%2C%20but%20later%20he%20was%20beaten%20and%20shot%2C%20Rupinder%20has%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnAnandpal's%20story%20has%20gripped%20Rajasthan%20for%20nearly%20three%20decades.%20The%20son%20of%20a%20police%20constable%2C%20Anandpal%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20teacher%2C%20but%20got%20into%20student%20politics%20and%20then%20into%20crime.%20He%20had%20contested%20two%20panchayat%20elections%20--%20one%20for%20a%20panchayat%20samiti%20post%20and%20later%20for%20Pradhan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20entry%20into%20politics%20led%20him%20to%20confrontations%20with%20local%20politicians%2C%20the%20police%20and%20in%20the%20caste%20faultlines%20of%20Rajasthan%2C%20he%20began%20to%20emerge%20as%20something%20of%20a%20Robin%20Hood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20more%20than%20three%20dozen%20cases%20of%20murder%20and%20extortion%20against%20Anandpal.%20He%20escaped%20from%20police%20custody%20in%20September%202015%20while%20returning%20from%20a%20court%20hearing%20to%20Ajmer%20high%20security%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20led%20to%20a%20two-year%20manhunt.%20Anandpal%20carried%20the%20highest%20reward%20ever%20for%20any%20gangster%20in%20Rajasthan%20--%20Rs%205%C2%A0%20lakh%2C%20and%20when%20the%20police%20finally%20gunned%20him%20down%20on%20July%2024%2C%202017%2C%20there%20was%20a%20huge%20public%20outcry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20family%20refused%20to%20cremate%20his%20body%20and%20it%20had%20to%20be%20kept%20in%20a%20freezer%20for%20over%20three%20weeks%20as%20the%20government%20tried%20to%20handle%20the%20political%20protests%20that%20followed%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%20the%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20government%20handed%20over%20the%20investigation%20to%20the%20CBI.%20But%20today%2C%20a%20Jodhpur%20court%20rejected%20the%20closure%20report%20of%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20with%20four%20police%20officers%20under%20scanner%20for%20the%20encounter%2C%20the%20gangster%20is%20back%20in%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajasthan's%20home%20minister%20Jawahar%20Singh%20Bedam%20has%20so%20far%20refused%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20court's%20decision.%20The%20next%20hearing%20of%20the%20case%20is%20on%20October%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721831400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fffshcq2o_gangster_625x300_24_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcops-involved-in-anandpal-encounter-face-probe-court-rejects-cbi-report-6179867%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Rajasthan%20Police's%20role%20in%20the%20encounter%20of%20gangster%20Anandpal%20will%20be%20investigated%2C%20a%20special%20court%20in%20Jodhpur%20ruled%20today%2C%20rejecting%20the%20CBI's%20closure%20report%20of%202020.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcops-involved-in-anandpal-encounter-face-probe-court-rejects-cbi-report-6179867%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcops-involved-in-anandpal-encounter-face-probe-court-rejects-cbi-report-6179867%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcops-involved-in-anandpal-encounter-face-probe-court-rejects-cbi-report-6179867%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22World%20Cup%20Final%20Pitch%20Was%20Doctored%3F%20Dravid's%20Coaching%20Staff%20Breaks%20Silence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20is%20currently%20riding%20the%20high%20of%20of%20the%202024%20T20%20World%20Cup%20triumph.%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20his%20men%20ended%20a%2011-year%20drought%20for%20an%20ICC%20title%20by%20beating%20South%20Africa%20in%20the%20final.%20However%2C%20few%20months%20ago%20the%20situation%20was%20completely%20different.%20India%2C%20seemingly%20invincible%20till%20that%20stage%2C%20lost%20to%20Australia%20in%20the%20final%20of%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%202023%20in%20Ahmedabad.%20If%20the%20loss%20was%20not%20enough%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20later%2C%20former%20India%20star%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mohammad%20Kaif%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F247-mohammad-kaif-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMohammad%20Kaif%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20pitch%20had%20been%20deliberately%20made%20slow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20there%20for%20three%20days.%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rahul%20Dravid%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F174-rahul-dravid-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERahul%20Dravid%3C%2Fa%3E%20inspected%20the%20pitch%20every%20day%20for%203%20days%20ahead%20of%20the%20final.%20They%20stood%20beside%20the%20pitch%20for%20an%20hour%20every%20day.%20I%20saw%20the%20pitch%20change%20its%20colour.%20There%20was%20no%20watering%20the%20pitch%2C%20no%20grass%20on%20the%20track.%20India%20wanted%20to%20give%20Australia%20a%20slow%20track.%20This%20is%20the%20truth%2C%20even%20if%20people%20don't%20want%20to%20believe%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaif%20said%20on%20Lallantop%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Viram%20Rathour%2C%20ex-batting%20coach%20of%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%2C%20who%20was%20there%20for%20both%20T20%20World%20Cup%202014%20and%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%202023%2C%20broke%20his%20silence%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20heard%20this%20story%20that%20the%20pitch%20was%20different%2C%20which%20I%20don't%20agree%20with%20at%20all.%20We%20played%20on%20similar%20wickets%20in%20the%20earlier%20matches%20as%20well.%20Matches%20against%20Australia%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20England%20were%20also%20played%20on%20slow%20pitches.%20The%20Ahmedabad%20pitch%2C%20however%2C%20eased%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Rathour%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsportstar.thehindu.com%2Fcricket%2Fvikram-rathour-interview-batting-coach-t20-world-cup-win-barbados-australia-36-all-out-indian-cricket-news%2Farticle68440594.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESportstar%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20India%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20who%20won%20the%20toss%20and%20opted%20to%20bat%20first.%20Australia%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Pat%20Cummins%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1656-pat-cummins-playerprofile%5C%22%3EPat%20Cummins%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20was%20happy%20to%20bowl%20first%2C%20knowing%20that%20the%20pitch%20is%20likely%20to%20get%20better%20as%20the%20day%20progressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20feeling%20was%20that%20Australia%20had%20Pat%20Cummins%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mitchell%20Starc%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1416-mitchell-starc-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMitchell%20Starc%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20India%20wanted%20to%20give%20a%20slow%20pitch%2C%20and%20that%20was%20our%20mistake.%20Many%20people%20say%20that%20curators%20do%20their%20own%20thing%20and%20we%20don't%20influence%20-%20that%20is%20rubbish.%20When%20you%20are%20moving%20around%20the%20pitch%20-%20you%20have%20to%20say%20just%20two%20lines%20-%20please%20don't%20put%20water%2C%20just%20reduce%20the%20grass.%20This%20happens.%20That%20is%20truth.%20And%20it%20should%20be%20done.%20You%20are%20playing%20at%20home.%20And%20we%20did%20it%20a%20little%20too%20much%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaif%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721830920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fm0rhahco_rahul-dravid_625x300_02_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fworld-cup-final-pitch-was-doctored-rahul-dravids-indian-cricket-team-coaching-staff-breaks-silence-6179810%22%2C%22summary%22%3A