20Mumbai%20Police%20in%20a%20court%20here%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20heard%20a%20firecracker-like%20sound%20while%20being%20asleep%20at%20his%20residence%20in%20Galaxy%20Apartments%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20April%2014%2C%20Mr%20Khan%20told%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20police%20bodyguard%20told%20him%20around%204.55%20am%20that%20two%20people%20on%20motorbike%20had%20fired%20at%20the%20first-floor%20balcony%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20had%20been%20attempts%20to%20hurt%20him%20and%20his%20family%20earlier%2C%20Mr%20Khan%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20his%20bodyguard%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20regarding%20the%20firing%20at%20Bandra%20police%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20learnt%20later%20that%20gangster%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20and%20his%20brother%20Anmol%20Bishnoi%20had%20confessed%20and%20taken%20responsibility%20of%20the%20attack%20in%20a%20Facebook%20post%2C%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELawrence%20Bishnoi%20and%20his%20gang%20members%20had%20talked%20about%20killing%20Mr%20Khan%20and%20his%20relatives%20earlier%20too%2C%20the%20statement%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20I%20believe%20that%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20his%20gang%20members%2C%20carried%20out%20the%20firing%20incident%20when%20my%20family%20members%20were%20sleeping%20and%20(they%20were)%20planning%20to%20kill%20me%20and%20my%20family%20members.%26quot%3B%20He%20and%20his%20family%20had%20received%20several%20other%20threats%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20the%20actor%20told%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20a%20threat%20letter%20was%20found%20on%20a%20bench%20opposite%20his%20building%2C%20while%20in%20March%202023%2C%20they%20received%20an%20email%20threat%20from%20the%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20unidentified%20persons%20tried%20to%20trespass%20into%20his%20farmhouse%20near%20Panvel%20using%20fake%20identities%20in%20January%202024%2C%20the%20actor%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20filed%20the%201%2C735-page%20charge%20sheet%20in%20the%20firing%20case%20before%20the%20special%20court%20for%20Maharashtra%20Control%20of%20Organised%20Crime%20Act%20cases%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20recently%20took%20cognizance%20of%20the%20charge%20sheet%2C%20saying%20that%20prima%20facie%20there%20was%20enough%20material%20to%20proceed%20against%20the%20six%20arrested%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20arrested%20in%20the%20case%20were%20Vickykumar%20Gupta%2C%20Sagarkumar%20Pal%2C%20Sonukumar%20Bishnoi%2C%20Anujkumar%20Thapan%20(now%20dead)%2C%20Mohd%20Rafiq%20Choudhary%20and%20Harpal%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThapan%20allegedly%20committed%20suicide%20in%20police%20custody%20after%20his%20arrest.%20The%20other%20five%20are%20now%20in%20judicial%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721829480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fm93dpf4g_salman-khan-_625x300_03_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flawrence-bishnoi-gang-wanted-to-kill-me-and-my-family-salman-khan-to-cops-6179619%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bollywood%20actor%20Salman%20Khan%20has%20told%20police%20that%20he%20believed%20the%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang%20carried%20out%20the%20firing%20at%20his%20residence%20in%20Mumbai%20in%20April%20this%20year%20with%20the%20intention%20to%20kill%20him%20and%20his%20family%20members.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flawrence-bishnoi-gang-wanted-to-kill-me-and-my-family-salman-khan-to-cops-6179619%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flawrence-bishnoi-gang-wanted-to-kill-me-and-my-family-salman-khan-to-cops-6179619%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flawrence-bishnoi-gang-wanted-to-kill-me-and-my-family-salman-khan-to-cops-6179619%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Still%20Wasting%20AC%20Water%3F%20This%20Housing%20Society%20Saves%205000%20Litres%2FDay%20With%20a%20Brilliant%20Idea%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEvery%20drop%20of%20water%20counts.%20This%20should%20be%20a%20mantra%20for%20everyone%20as%20the%20world%20faces%20a%20severe%20water%20shortage.%20Do%20you%20know%20how%20much%20water%20is%20used%20every%20time%20you%20flush%3F%20In%20older%20toilets%20installed%20in%20India%2C%20almost%20five%20to%20ten%20litres%20of%20water%20are%20used%20per%20flush.%20For%20a%20family%20of%20four%20using%20the%20toilet%20at%20least%20three%20times%20a%20day%20each%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20a%20staggering%203%2C600%20litres%20of%20water%20per%20month!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20newer%20toilets%20come%20with%20low%20flush%20options%2C%20what%20can%20people%20with%20older%20toilets%20do%3F%20This%20question%20troubled%20the%20residents%20and%20management%20committee%20members%20of%20Saprem%20Co-operative%20Housing%20Society%20in%20Thane%2C%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThane%2C%20like%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20has%20been%20facing%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F346766%2Fdate-farming-in-india-rajasthan-farmer-rainwater-harvesting-earns-lakhs-by-growing-award-winning-dates-organically%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emajor%20water%20crisis%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20recent%20years.%20With%20reservoirs%20drying%20up%2C%20the%20Brihanmumbai%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(BMC)%20announced%20a%2010%20percent%20water%20cut%20starting%20in%20June%202024%20to%20conserve%20the%20available%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20also%20impacted%20the%20water%20supply%20to%20the%20Thane%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(TMC).%20Consequently%2C%20it%20is%20now%20up%20to%20citizens%20to%20take%20action%2C%20both%20individually%20and%20collectively%2C%20particularly%20in%20gated%20communities%20and%20housing%20societies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20relying%20solely%20on%20the%20water%20supplied%20by%20the%20TMC%20and%20purchasing%20additional%20tankers%2C%20the%20residents%20of%20Saprem%20CHS%20decided%20to%20become%20self-sufficient%20in%20their%20water%20needs.%20How%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%20on%20to%20find%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20panacea%20for%20water%20woes%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuilt%20in%201997%2C%20the%20society%20has%20two%20wings%20and%2064%20flats%20in%20total.%20Over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20residents%20grappled%20with%20major%20water%20shortages.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20several%20days%20when%20we%20had%20water%20supply%20only%20for%20an%20hour%20or%20so.%20We%20also%20had%20to%20call%20for%20a%20water%20tanker%20from%20outside%2C%20paying%20thousands%20of%20rupees%20every%20day.%20It%20was%20a%20very%20difficult%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20Avinash%20Shaligram%2C%20secretary%2C%20Saprem%20CHS%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20was%20exacerbated%20in%20households%20where%20everyone%20would%20go%20to%20work%20or%20school%20and%20return%20to%20no%20water.%20After%20enduring%20this%20ordeal%20for%20months%2C%20the%20residents%20began%20brainstorming%20and%20coming%20up%20with%20different%20solutions.%20One%20thing%20was%20clear%20%E2%80%94%20they%20wanted%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F290271%2Fmumbai-rain-man-makes-rainwater-harvesting-system-using-low-cost-innovation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esave%20water%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20any%20way%20they%20could.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20society%20has%20a%20water%20tank%20with%20a%20capacity%20of%2020%2C000%20litres.%20As%20they%20started%20breaking%20down%20the%20basics%20of%20water%20usage%20in%20their%20households%2C%20one%20number%20stood%20out%20%E2%80%94%20the%20amount%20of%20water%20used%20in%20the%20toilets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem2-1721819754.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20rooftop%20rainwater%20harvesting%20system%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem2-1721819754.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem2-1721819754-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem2-1721819754-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem2-1721819754-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem2-1721819754-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358280%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20rooftop%20rainwater%20harvesting%20system%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20found%20that%20every%20time%20we%20flush%20the%20toilet%2C%20it%20uses%20five%20litres%20of%20water.%20In%20a%20household%20of%20four%20members%20who%20each%20use%20the%20washroom%20four%20times%20a%20day%2C%20it%20amounts%20to%2080%20litres%20of%20water%20per%20day.%20For%20the%20entire%20society%2C%20that%20was%20a%20whopping%205%2C120%20litres%20of%20water%20per%20day%2C%20more%20than%201%2F4th%20of%20the%20tank%E2%80%99s%20capacity%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Shaligram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20wondered%20how%20to%20prevent%20this%20natural%20resource%20from%20being%20%E2%80%98flushed%E2%80%99%20down!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20find%20an%20alternative%20water%20source%2C%20they%20conducted%20a%20geological%20survey%20and%20dug%20a%20borewell.%20They%20struck%20water%20350%20feet%20below%20the%20surface%20and%20began%20using%20this%20water%20for%20their%20toilets.%20This%20immediately%20solved%20their%20water%20woes%2C%20providing%20a%2024-hour%20water%20supply!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20stopping%20there%2C%20the%20residents%20sought%20a%20way%20to%20recharge%20the%20groundwater.%20To%20this%20end%2C%20they%20built%20a%20rainwater%20harvesting%20system.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20rainwater%20that%20was%20being%20collected%20on%20the%20terrace%20was%20going%20to%20waste%2C%20in%20a%20drain.%20We%20wanted%20a%20system%20that%20would%20collect%20this%20water%20and%20divert%20it%20into%20the%20borewell%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Arun%20Deshmukh%2C%20management%20committee%20member%2C%20Saprem%20CHS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20it%20works%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECorrugated%20sheets%20have%20been%20installed%20on%20the%20rooftop%20with%20bars%20on%20the%20side.%20Eight%20pipes%20have%20been%20fixed%20across%20the%20length%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F289205%2Frainwater-harvesting-system-in-tamil-nadu-helps-village-during-cyclone%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erooftop%20to%20collect%20rainwater%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20pipes%20are%20connected%20to%20pipes%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20channel%20the%20water%20to%20the%20borewell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-25-1721828440.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-25-1721828440.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-25-1721828440-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-25-1721828440-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-25-1721828440-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-25-1721828440-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358388%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstalled%20almost%20three%20years%20ago%2C%20this%20system%20has%20made%20the%20residents%20self-sufficient%20and%20prevents%20rainwater%20from%20going%20to%20waste.%20They%20have%20been%20using%20this%20water%20for%20their%20toilet%20needs%20and%20are%20now%20exploring%20ways%20to%20use%20it%20for%20other%20purposes.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20the%20water%20tested%20but%20it%20was%20unfit%20for%20other%20use.%20We%20are%20getting%20it%20tested%20again%20now%20to%20see%20if%20it%20can%20at%20least%20be%20used%20for%20washing%20clothes%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shaligram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESaving%20AC%20Water%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20this%20solution%20produced%20phenomenal%20results%2C%20the%20eager%20residents%20looked%20for%20further%20ways%20to%20save%20water.%20Another%20significant%20source%20of%20water%20wastage%20was%20the%20water%20from%20air%20conditioners%20(ACs).%20Almost%20every%20house%20in%20the%20society%20has%20an%20AC%2C%20says%20Deshmukh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20summers%2C%20these%20ACs%20run%20all%20night%20and%20for%20long%20hours%20during%20the%20day%2C%20especially%20on%20weekends%20and%20in%20work-from-home%20situations.%20Generally%2C%20a%20one-tonne%20air%20conditioner%20produces%2010%20litres%20of%20water%20if%20used%20for%20eight%20hours%20%E2%80%94%20with%20this%20amount%20increasing%20based%20on%20the%20size%20of%20the%20AC.%20To%20prevent%20this%20condensate%2