0Ashok%2C%20and%20Vikram%20Kumar%2C%20we%20sat%20down%20with%20Pranjal%20to%20understand%20how%20they%20are%20revolutionising%20the%20legal%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAn%20idea%20to%20resolve%20year-long%20disputes%20online%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Vikram%20pursued%20higher%20education%20in%20computer%20science%2C%20Pranjal%20and%20Akshetha%20studied%20law.%20In%202015%2C%20Vikram%20and%20Pranjal%2C%20who%20was%20then%20a%20second-year%20law%20student%20at%20the%20West%20Bengal%20National%20University%20of%20Juridical%20Sciences%2C%20met%20at%20the%20Startup%20Weekend%20event%20hosted%20by%20IIM-Calcutta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20of%20us%20came%20with%20a%20startup%20idea.%20I%20envisioned%20working%20on%20an%20Online%20Dispute%20Resolution%20(ODR)%20system%20that%20could%20reduce%20the%20dependency%20on%20courts%20which%20are%20already%20burdened%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F34596%2Fsupreme-court-launches-portal-to-track-pending-cases%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebacklog%20of%20cases%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pranjal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20he%20got%20JAMS%20Weinstein%20International%20Fellowship%20opportunity%20as%20part%20of%20which%20he%20attended%20the%20mediation%20training%20course%20at%20Harvard%20Law%20School%20and%20the%20Business%20Development%20Course%20at%20the%20Stanford%20Graduate%20Business%20School.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20always%20fond%20of%20mediation.%20This%20three-month%20long%20fellowship%20allowed%20me%20to%20observe%20the%20online%20dispute%20resolution%20and%20case%20management%20concepts%20in%20the%20US.%20Back%20at%20home%20in%20India%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Etareekh-pe-tareekh%20%3C%2Fem%3E(chronic%20delay%20in%20judicial%20proceedings)%20hinders%20justice.%20I%20wanted%20to%20reduce%20the%20burden%20on%20courts%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Pranjal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20the%20trio%20launched%20Sama%20%E2%80%93%20meaning%20to%20ask%20and%20advise%20others.%20Sama%20is%20based%20on%20%3Cem%3Esaam%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%93%20one%20of%20the%20four%20laws%20in%20Chanakya%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Eneeti%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3Esaam%20%3C%2Fem%3E(persuade)%2C%3Cem%3E%20daam%20%3C%2Fem%3E(purchase)%2C%20%3Cem%3Edand%20%3C%2Fem%3E(punish)%2C%20%3Cem%3Ebhed%20%3C%2Fem%3E(exploit%20the%20weakness).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FSama-3-1721387466.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sama%20has%20resolved%20more%20than%2035%20lakh%20cases%20out%20of%20court%20and%20cost-effectively.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FSama-3-1721387466.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FSama-3-1721387466-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FSama-3-1721387466-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FSama-3-1721387466-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FSama-3-1721387466-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357676%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESama%20has%20resolved%20more%20than%2035%20lakh%20cases%20out%20of%20court%20and%20cost-effectively.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20focuses%20on%20resolving%20civil%20disputes%20such%20as%20banking%2C%20financial%2C%20insurance%20sector%2C%20broker%20disputes%2C%20and%20security%20market.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20work%20with%20Lok%20Adalats%20which%20manages%20disputes%20related%20to%20challan%20and%20electricity%20bill%2C%20accidental%20insurance%2C%20and%20cheque%20bounce%20cases%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pranjal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20functioning%20of%20their%20startup%2C%20Pranjal%20informs%20that%20firstly%20the%20grievant%20registers%20on%20the%20website%20and%20then%20files%20their%20cases.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThereafter%2C%20the%20team%20invites%20the%20other%20party%20through%20email%2C%20phone%20number%2C%20and%20sends%20a%20notice%20through%20courier%20for%20out%20of%20court%20settlement.%20Soon%2C%20an%20experienced%20mediator%20is%20appointed%20to%20speak%20to%20both%20parties%20and%20tries%20to%20arrive%20at%20a%20%3Cem%3Erajinama%20%3C%2Fem%3E(settlement)%20between%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20try%20to%20complete%20this%20process%20within%2030%20days.%20After%20this%2C%20we%20design%20a%20settlement%20agreement%20and%20take%20signatures%20of%20both%20parties%20and%20mediators.%20It%20has%20the%20same%20value%20as%20the%20decree%20of%20the%20court.%20The%20only%20difference%20is%20that%20it%20requires%20three%20years%20in%20court%20whereas%2030%20days%20with%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Pranjal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20the%20settlement%20does%20not%20occur%20at%20the%20mediation%20level%2C%20the%20case%20goes%20for%20arbitration.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20mediation%20cannot%20pass%20a%20judgement%20and%20only%20strive%20for%20settlement%2C%20arbitration%20gives%20the%20final%20judgement.%20The%20case%20in%20arbitration%20gets%20resolved%20within%2090%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20Pranjal%20says%2C%20private%20parties%20can%20resolve%20disputes%20provided%20they%20comply%20with%20the%20Mediation%20Act%202023%20and%20the%20Arbitration%20and%20Conciliation%20Act%2C%201996.%20The%20startup%20also%20received%20recognition%20from%20the%20former%20Union%20Minister%20of%20Law%20and%20Justice%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20for%20promoting%C2%A0%20ODR%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FSy4Nk4q2eNg%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26rel%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D1%26controls%3D1%26color%3Dred%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20the%20startup%20has%20onboarded%20more%20than%203%2C000%20arbitrators%20with%20at%20least%2010%20years%20experience%20and%20mediators%20with%20at%20least%20five%20years%20of%20legal%20experience%20across%20443%20districts%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EReducing%20the%20burden%20on%20courts%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20got%20its%20first%20client%20in%202019.%20Between%202015%20and%202018%2C%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20get%20any%20cases.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20understand%20the%20word%20mediation.%20They%20would%20confuse%20it%20with%20meditation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20laughs%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20we%20worked%20a%20lot%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20ODR.%20We%20organised%20%3Cem%3Enukkad%20natak%3C%2Fem%3Es%20and%20campaigns%20like%20%3Cem%3Esuljhao%20magar%20pyaar%20se%20%3C%2Fem%3E(resolve%20with%20love)%2C%20used%20flash%20mobs%2C%20and%20distributed%20pamphlets.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFast%20forward%20to%202024%2C%20they%20have%20solved%20more%20than%2035%20lakh%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20Sama%20assists%20the%20clients%20online%2C%20Pranjal%20says%20they%20appoint%20a%20case%20manager%20to%20